    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《猫猫虫乐园》是一款轻松有趣的放置游戏，点击场景中央的魔法阵可以召唤出各种有独特形象和设定的猫猫虫，收集场景中猫猫虫们掉落的爪爪球，可以解锁更多风格的场景、有趣的功能和经典的小游戏，以及召唤更多的猫猫虫。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/2d9aea08573386c260ee2eab7f0a84ef.avif?t=1728457428\" width=462 height=174 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >点击Q弹魔法阵，召唤可爱猫猫虫</h2>出来吧！超稀有的猫猫虫！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/6e5d48c26dc7952aed7beb7b767b57be.avif?t=1728457428\" width=300 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超解压的收取爪爪球</h2>放开那个爪爪球，让我来！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/4760fb5aaeed9f9a4432c7137a10a739.avif?t=1728457428\" width=300 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >70+可爱有趣独特的猫猫虫</h2>可爱的外观，独特的设定，温馨、有趣的对白，超多的梗<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/2de7749d89f94284fce0281573c074e6.avif?t=1728457428\" width=300 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >10+经典小游戏和功能</h2>刮刮乐、2048、电子木鱼......<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/b88de5537a6be24f68e66433a829515e.avif?t=1728457428\" width=300 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多惊喜特殊时间的特别事件？</h2>更多内容持续更新</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244090/extras/ccfcfdf5db784d477d3e8430ea265c7b.avif?t=1728457428\" width=300 height=200 /></span>",
